From: Alice
To: Team
Subject: Re: Project Updates

Thanks for the updates. A few things:

@Bob - can you finalize the API documentation by next Friday? The current draft is missing the authentication section.
@Carol - please schedule a demo with the client for next week. They want to see the new features.
@Dave - the security review needs to be completed before we can launch. Let's aim for end of month.

Also, I'll handle the budget review for the steering committee meeting on the 15th.

Best,
Alice
